{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Dough","content":["Place 50 g water, sugar and yeast in mixing bowl then warm <nobr>2 min\/37°C\/speed 2<\/nobr>. Meanwhile, grease a large bowl with oil.","Add remaining 170 g water, oil, bread flour, spelt flour and salt then knead <nobr>1 min 30 sec\/<\/nobr>. Transfer dough to prepared bowl, cover with cling film then set aside to rise in a warm place until doubled in size (approx. 1-2 hours)."]},{"title":"Topping","content":["Towards end of rising time, preheat oven to 220°C and line a large baking tray with baking paper.","Place salt, chicory and oil in mixing bowl then cook <nobr>8 min\/Varoma\/\/speed 1<\/nobr>. Transfer cooked chicory to simmering basket and set aside to drain and cool.","Transfer risen dough to prepared baking tray. Use fingertips to spread dough out to the size of the tray, with a slightly thicker edge.","Arrange reserved cooked chicory over dough then Taleggio and nuts over the top. Bake for 15-20 minutes (220°C) until edges are golden. Serve hot, cut in slices."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Dough","content":["220 g water","1 tsp sugar","2 tsp dried instant yeast","30 g extra virgin olive oil, plus extra for greasing","200 g strong white bread flour","200 g spelt flour","1 ½ tsp fine sea salt"]},{"title":"Topping","content":["2 - 3 pinches fine sea salt, to taste","450 g chicory, quartered","20 g extra virgin olive oil","200 g Taleggio, rind removed, cut in pieces (2 cm)","10 - 15 g shelled walnuts, in pieces"]}],"id":"r131924","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-f_7sfvH8iS8\/XZaoRHBmD_I\/AAAAAAAAhIg\/LsbrvPrCehsyds3y05mp4N8iW8fO08XzACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_irptUbdfdknVCdwz.png","title":"Spelt Flour Pizza with Chicory and Taleggio","publishedAt":"2016-09-12T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"26.6 g","fat":"39.7 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"75.8 g","calories":"3130 kJ \/ 748 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large bowl, cling film, large baking tray, baking paper, oven","hintsAndTric